        <updateDate>2007-08-23T19:55:11Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow parents of a murdered child to continue to claim a personal tax exemption for such child for five years after the death of such child or the date on which such child would have attained the age of 18, whichever is earlier. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
